{"tid":2141493,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日撘巴士比個廢老問我幾錢","createTime":"2020-08-05T17:12:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T17:37:44.000Z","uid":46869,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"db9a1cf5dcbc30140ab94366319afd73e8c933d3","tid":2141493,"uid":46869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T17:12:18.000Z","msg":"今日九點幾撘巴士，上咗車之後有個廢老係到揾銀仔，之後問我: <br />\n<br />\n「小姐，依程車幾錢？我眼差睇唔多清楚」<br />\n<br />\n本身以為又係個啲5蚊黨，周圍呃人錢。之後我話: <br />\n<br />\n「9.8，你唔夠散紙？我都無喎」<br />\n<br />\n之後佢話: <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「咩9.8啊？我老人家嚟，兩蚊啊！」<br />\n<br />\n屌！我即刻屌咗岀聲啊！仆街！咁你又問？你撘乜撚都兩蚊架啦，我屌你！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4f725b000d0eda899fecf3bb46dfca297ed98ed","tid":2141493,"uid":252142,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T17:13:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"551263cf36c47abfa733bb900f2a3106574484f2","tid":2141493,"uid":27416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T17:14:29.000Z","msg":"你唔係1000過夜咩"},{"pid":"9cdf3f79059c7a8b8c51fa72d918b65c9c3dd0f7","tid":2141493,"uid":204429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T17:14:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑左 多謝提供笑話一則"},{"pid":"ea2343856cab20d541982ee539bdfebe45f27260","tid":2141493,"ui